            </div>
            <div class="relative z-10 px-12 max-w-5xl">
                <span
                    class="inline-block px-4 py-1 mb-6 bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container font-headline font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs">
                    ESTABLISHED 1958
                </span>
                <h1
                    class="text-7xl md:text-9xl font-black font-headline text-white leading-none uppercase tracking-tighter mb-8">
                    Built for <br /><span class="text-primary-container">Precision.</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-surface-container max-w-2xl font-light leading-relaxed">
                    A legacy of structural integrity, engineering excellence, and a 100% employee-owned commitment
                    to
                    every foundation we lay.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 w-24 h-24 hazard-gradient opacity-20"></div>
        </section>
        <!-- History & Grid Layout -->
        <section class="py-32 px-12 bg-surface blueprint-grid">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16">
                <div class="lg:col-span-5">
                    <h2
                        class="text-5xl font-black font-headline text-on-surface uppercase tracking-tighter mb-12 border-l-8 border-primary pl-8">
                        Our History
                    </h2>
                    <div class="space-y-8 text-lg text-secondary leading-loose">
                        <p>Starting as a small family masonry firm in 1958, PC Construction has evolved into one of
                            the
                            nation's most respected employee-owned construction companies.</p>
                        <p>For over six decades, we have scaled our operations to manage complex projects across the
                            commercial, industrial, and infrastructure sectors, never losing sight of the technical
                            precision required for lasting structures.</p>
                        <div class="pt-8">
                            <div class="text-7xl font-black text-primary/10 font-headline leading-none">65+</div>
                            <div class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary mt-2">Years of
                                Engineering Mastery</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="lg:col-span-7 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <img class="w-full aspect-square object-cover grayscale"
                            data-alt="Black and white archival photo of construction workers on a vintage steel frame building site"
                            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC8qbZY0PAIlAy-DTX6dJYKOVqb9A8UTOeSNSgYI8zKeJWUTJK4-aMAn5qk_lbwJg3qjKHPtREBvR-W61gbh661GZy8ArtR5R1vlEgTn-_-AF7rvPayrFe79NxwBuOVvmkdFu8pMNCOaV34xCKhADdGnrkeZ1XAaVwGFja1abP0M6icLQPesauT6s7k-EcfypK0RlTGMLLOgG1-ZbYNwePs2dCRc4L99r2tF-9kU7VyyU-USK8a-yeOK3rZyZDe7XcxPuzl-XkRxFU" />
                        <div class="bg-surface-container-highest p-8">
                            <h3 class="font-headline font-bold uppercase text-xl mb-2">1958</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-secondary uppercase tracking-wider leading-relaxed">Foundation
                                laid
                                as Pizzagalli Construction Company.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-4 mt-12">
                        <div class="bg-inverse-surface p-8 text-white">
                            <h3 class="font-headline font-bold uppercase text-xl mb-2 text-primary-container">2009
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-sm opacity-80 uppercase tracking-wider leading-relaxed">Transitioned to
                                100%
                                employee ownership via ESOP.</p>
                        </div>
                        <img class="w-full aspect-[3/4] object-cover"
                            data-alt="Modern high-angle view of a large water treatment plant construction project with complex piping and concrete basins"
                            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCsgn--ER1dWbZMmI4Jy23_pVNLOqePagnJ-p_H2WopZosKqxXD6dStnVizTNczY2XiHZvn93-KPXIwqp6lyMmVCbDQZZc0GN-bYpOYpio018fQbdanXv0bTljCIHw-6xlUS23uhFpxCJbJnX-u-d7g2LrvmDOaUYk4Sq_KmDQU5nOvMd8X99yUVuAT_BTybLCiC1pjK-otb9ioaZI-YgcR4VLJmcq7hLDFXaSLEqR9WftqxcODwJIUsMF8UmRUfwVYeurRVxk-Mgk" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <!-- Values Section - Bento Grid -->
        <section class="py-32 bg-inverse-surface text-white">
            <div class="px-12 mb-20 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-8">
                <div>
                    <span
                        class="text-primary-container font-headline font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm block mb-4">//
                        CORE PRINCIPLES</span>
                    <h2 class="text-6xl font-black font-headline uppercase tracking-tighter">The Steel Framework
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <p class="text-surface-container-highest max-w-md text-lg font-light">
                    Our values aren't just words on a wall; they are the technical specifications for how we conduct
                    business.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-stone-800 border-y border-stone-800">
                <!-- Value 1 -->
                <div class="bg-inverse-surface p-12 group hover:bg-stone-800 transition-colors">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary-container"
                            style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">precision_manufacturing</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3
                        class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline uppercase mb-6 group-hover:text-primary-container transition-colors">
                        Uncompromising Precision</h3>
                    <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed uppercase text-sm tracking-widest">Accuracy is our
                        baseline. From the first bid to the final bolt, we execute with surgical technical
                        discipline.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <!-- Value 2 -->
                <div class="bg-inverse-surface p-12 group hover:bg-stone-800 transition-colors">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary-container"
                            style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">shield_with_heart</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3
                        class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline uppercase mb-6 group-hover:text-primary-container transition-colors">
                        Safety First. Always.</h3>
                    <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed uppercase text-sm tracking-widest">Our goal is zero
                        incidents. We invest heavily in safety protocols that exceed federal standards to protect
                        our
                        owners.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- Value 3 -->
                <div class="bg-inverse-surface p-12 group hover:bg-stone-800 transition-colors">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary-container"
                            style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">groups</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3
                        class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline uppercase mb-6 group-hover:text-primary-container transition-colors">
                        Radical Ownership</h3>
                    <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed uppercase text-sm tracking-widest">As 100%
                        employee-owners,
                        every individual is incentivized to ensure the highest quality and client satisfaction.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <!-- Employee Ownership / Culture -->
        <section class="py-32 px-12 bg-surface-container-low overflow-hidden relative">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-20">
