                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-secondary mb-10 leading-loose">
                        PC Construction is 100% employee-owned. This isn't just a financial structure; it's our
                        identity. When you work with us, you're working with partners who have a direct stake in the
                        project's success. This fosters a culture of accountability, innovation, and pride that
                        traditional firms simply cannot replicate.
                    </p>
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <span class="text-primary font-black font-headline text-2xl">01/</span>
                            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Total transparency in operations
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <span class="text-primary font-black font-headline text-2xl">02/</span>
                            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Shared rewards for project
                                milestones
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <span class="text-primary font-black font-headline text-2xl">03/</span>
                            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Lifelong career development
                                tracks
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
